                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6208" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1569</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8447 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">维维股份：多元化“折戟”能否再“欢乐开怀”？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">V V Food &amp; Beverage:Can it be happy again after the failure of diversification?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘艳华，刘晓静</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">维维食品饮料股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">维维股份；多元化战略；发展战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">V V Food &amp; Beverage; Diversification strategy; Development Strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2000年6月维维股份上市，凭借着“维维豆奶，欢乐开怀”的广告语，“维维”牌豆奶粉火爆全国，成为我国的“豆奶大王”，很长时间内都稳坐豆奶行业第一的位置。上市后维维股份专注多元化经营，涉足多个行业但都经营失败，豆奶业务市场份额连续下降，2021年4月被实施风险警告，维维集团将绝大部分股票转让给新盛集团。作为曾经的“豆奶大王”，维维股份怎么会沦落到这种地步？本案例在梳理维维股份多元化发展过程的基础上，重点描述了多元化战略给其带来的风险和挑战，帮助学生深入理解多元化战略的动机、适用条件、分类、优缺点、成败影响因素等知识点，并引导学生思考企业发展战略，以培养其分析和解决问题的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> In June 2000, V V Food &amp; Beverage (hereinafter referred to as VVFB) listed on the stock market. With the slogan &quot;V V Soy Milk, Happy &quot;, &quot;V V&quot; brand soy milk powder became popular in China and became &quot;King of soy milk&quot;,taking the first position in the soy milk industry for a long time. After listing, VVFB focused on diversified operations, involved in multiple industries but failed to operate.The market share of the soy milk business continued to decline. A risk warning was implemented in April 2021. V V Group transferred most of its shares to XinSheng Group. As the former &quot;King of soy milk&quot;, how can VVFB have fallen to this point? On the basis of combing the diversified development process of VVFB, this case focuses on the risks and challenges brought by the diversification strategy. It helps students to deeply understand the motivation, applicable conditions, classification, advantages and disadvantages ,success and failure factors of the diversification strategy, and guides students to think about the company development strategy,to cultivate their  analytical and problem-solving skills.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业发展战略、企业多元化战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-03</td>
                            </tr>
